TITLE: WWE SummerSlam 2022: Brock Lesnar lifts ring with tractor, Logan Paul frog splashes The Miz, more highlights
SUMMARY: Roman Reigns retained the Undisputed WWE Universal Championship in an epic match with Brock Lesnar -- but it was just one of the many SummerSlam highlights.

TITLE: NBA legend Bill Russell dead at 88
SUMMARY: Bill Russell, one of the greatest NBA players of all time, has died, his family announced on Sunday. He was 88.

TITLE: DOJ admits spike in domestic terrorism investigations mostly related to Jan. 6 riots
SUMMARY: Assistant Attorney General Matt Olsen said that a large potion of the surge in domestic terrorism and extremist cases the DOJ counted are tied to the Capitol riots.

TITLE: White House physician says President Biden continues to test positive for COVID
SUMMARY: President Joe Biden continues to to test positive for COVID-19 after re-contracting the virus last week. Biden suffered moderate symptoms when he first got the virus.

TITLE: New Mexico unveils statues of ‘Breaking Bad’ meth cooks amid opioid crisis
SUMMARY: A New Mexico city unveiled statues of the meth cooks and dealers from 'Breaking Bad' on Friday as even the statues' donor admitted it might be sending a poor message.

TITLE: Toomey rips Dems trotting out ‘pseudo celebrity’ Jon Stewart to ‘make up false accusations’ about veteran bill
SUMMARY: Sen. Pat Toomey, R-Pa., on Sunday ripped Democrats and comedian Jon Stewart for trying to paint him as anti-veteran for blocking a veterans benefits bill last week.

TITLE: Pro Bowler Ryan Kerrigan hangs up his cleats after 11 seasons in the NFL
SUMMARY: Ryan Kerrigan announced his retirement on Friday at the age of 33. He leaves the NFL as the all-time sack leader for the Washington Commanders' franchise.

TITLE: Samuel Sandoval, among last Navajo Code Talkers, dies at 98
SUMMARY: Samuel Sandoval, one of the four remaining Navajo Code Talkers who helped the U.S. win the war against Japan in the Pacific during World War II, has died at 98.

TITLE: CNN panelist says legislative victories won't be enough for Dems in the midterms: 'Downtowns are still empty'
SUMMARY: A CNN panelist said Sunday that the recent Democratic legislative wins would not be enough for the party to hold on to a majority in the midterm elections.

TITLE: Manchin dodges on whether he wants Dems to control Congress, again declines to support Biden for 2024
SUMMARY: Appearing on multiple television programs Sunday morning, Sen. Joe Manchin refused to say whether he supported his fellow Democrats in upcoming elections.
